programme.title: Diari Ustaz
programme.desc: Diari Ustaz merupakan suatu rancangan yang akan mengenengahkan Ustaz tersohor negara didalam menyampaikan tazkirah dan panduan disertai hujah-hujah hadis dan Al Quran. Pengisian menjurus kepada permasalahan semasa masyarakat.

programme.title: Setia Menunggumu
programme.desc: Sebelum Adi berangkat, Adi telah memberitahu kenalan rapat nya yang dia akan pergi mencari ilmu agama jauh dari sini. Adi mengambil bas dan sampai ke pekan, sampai di pekan dia cuba menahan kereta yang lalu lalang, kemudian ada sebuah lori yang baik hati memberi dia tumpang sampai ke KL. Sampai sahaja di KL, Adi tidak tahu dia mahu pergi ke mana, lalu dia jumpa sebuah masjid tetapi dia tidak solat kerana Adi tidak tahu solat. Selesai habis solat di masjid itu, dia bertanyakan dari Imam masjid tersebut tentang cara untuk mempelajari ilmu agama. Imam tersebut telah memberikan nya nombor telefon seorang pemuda. Adi semakin hari semakin kehabisan wang, dia cuba untuk mencari kerja di warung-warung yang terdekat, tetapi tidak ada. Adi berehat di kaki lima, tiba-tiba datang dua orang samseng mendekatinya. Apakah yang akan terjadi dengan Adi? Apakah yang akan dilakukan oleh samseng tersebut kepada Adi?

programme.title: Puteri Gunung Ledang S1
programme.desc: Natasya hanya berkelulusan SPM tetapi bijak, agak lasak dan adakala lebih bersifat seperti lelaki. Namun sesekali dia berdandan dan bersolek, pastinya kebanyakan pemuda kampung akan terpikat dengan kecantikan yang dimiliki oleh Natasya dan memanggilnya Puteri Gunung Ledang. Natasya berimpian menjadi model terkenal. Setiap kali mencuba nasib, dia gagal dan akhirnya bekerja sebagai kerani di sebuah agensi peragaan sahaja. Nasibnya berubah apabila dia menjadi duta produk kecantikan secara tidak sengaja. Ramai yang mula jatuh hati dan terpikat pada kecantikan Natasya termasuklah majikannya Rayyan. Rayyan seorang lelaki yang kacak tetapi bersikap ‘kaki perempuan’. Mereka berkenalan secara lebih dekat tetapi Natasya meletakkan tujuh syarat untuk membuktikan cintanya.

programme.title: Selipar Jepun Stileto Merah
programme.desc: Roy semakin merasakan dirinya melakukan kesilapan untuk mengahwini Stila. Bersama-sama Datuk Azhar, dia berpakat untuk memperbaiki hubungan Leto dan Stila. Stila mendapat tahu akan hal itu dan kekal mahu meneruskan rancangan perkahwinan mereka. Namun, Roy enggan bersetuju dengan rancangan itu. Walaupun Airis tahu Leto masih menyimpan perasaan terhadap Stila, dia enggan melepaskan Leto dan tetap mahu meneruskan rancangan perkahwinan mereka. Pada hari perkahwinan itu, Leto mendapat panggilan telefon daripada Roy yang memberitahunya bahawa Stila akan ke luar negara. Leto cuba mengetepikan hal itu, namun, selepas Yani memdedahkan suatu rahsia besar kepada Leto, dia tahu bahawa dia harus bertemu Stila buat kali terakhirnya...

programme.title: Oh Fatimah
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Rahmat dan Fatimah yang sudah bercerai dan menunjuk-nunjuk antara satu sama lain bahawa mereka boleh mencari pengganti baru.

programme.title: Bakar S5
programme.desc: Bakar adalah sebuah rancangan masakan yang berkonsepkan makanan yang dimasak menggunakan ketuhar. Minggu ini, Adreena akan menyediakan dua resepi menarik iaitu Kek Baldu Merah versi Bebola dan Tat Lemon Meringue .

programme.title: Dapur Bujang S6
programme.desc: Dengan bajet RM10, Chef Naem, tukang masak Dapur Bujang akan menyediakan dua jenis hidangan masakan harian yang senang, sedap dan sihat. Untuk episod ini, Naem akan masak ikan masak asam & daging masak hitam.

programme.title: Jalan-Jalan Makan Angin (2019)
programme.desc: Memaparkan kedua-dua hos mengembara ke 101 Resort & Spa, Janda Baik, Pahang. Resort ini terkenal dengan pemandangan hutan dan sungai. Kedua-dua hos mengambil bahagian dalam aktiviti menunggang kuda di sana. Selepas itu hos menyambung pengembaraan ke Caravan Serai, Bentong, Pahang yang merupakan sebuah resort yang penuh dengan pokok buah-buahan seperti durian dan rambutan.

programme.title: Superhero Hati S1
programme.desc: Percutian singkat itu jadi lebih singkat apabila Zaza membawa Hjh. Fauziah dan Adam balik keesokan harinya. Rupanya dia tak tahan dengan kerenah Adam, manakala Adam pun tak suka dengan perangai plastik Zaza. Manakala Akasyah pula telah bertemu dengan Azmie, rakan sekolej yang turut mengenali Dahlia Suhana. Azmie terkejut bila dengar yang Suhana dah kurus dan cantik. Akasyah pula teringat kenangan lama, di mana dia jatuh hati dengan Dahlia selepas menyaksikan Suhana sering memberi kucing jalanan makan. Namun kehilangan Suhana secara tiba-tiba dari kolej, membuatkan Akasyah terluka. Azmie mengingatkan Akasyah agar melupakan Suhana kerana dia yakin Suhana telah mempunyai kekasih.

programme.title: Biar Aku Jadi Penunggu S1
programme.desc: Berikutan kereta Afeet rosak, dan dari segi tempat sukar memperolehi mekanik. Rafaal yang kebetulan tiba dan ingin membantu tetapi tidak jadi sebalik Afeet meninggi suara terhadap Iffat. Mujur bapa Afeet menemui mereka. Hubungan mereka masih dingin, malahan malam itu mereka juga tidur berasingan. Ibu Afeet yang terhidu gelagat mereka masih dingin terus menasihati Afeet agar memohon maaf dan bawa berbincang bersama. Kini, mereka seolah-olah saling tuduh menuduh tetapi yang jelas Afeet masih ada egonya. Di samping itu, Iffat menemui Hayati dan meluahkan rasa hati dan perasaaanya.

programme.title: Pelumba Malam
programme.desc: Kisah Inspektor Ema yang menyiasat latar belakang ketua kumpulan bermotosikal, Rizal dengan menyamar ingin rapat dengan Rizal.

programme.title: Jalan-Jalan Makan Angin (2019)
programme.desc: Hos Akhmal Nazri dan Atu Zero membawa penonton ke Village Le Jollax, Senai Johor. Mereka memperkenalkan kemudahan sedia ada di tempat peranginan tersebut, antaranya termasuk kolam renang, bilik karaoke dan wifi. Seterusnya kedua-dua hos melanjutkan pengembaraan mereka ke Midori Concept Hotel di Johor Bahru. Hotel berkonsep English Modern itu mempunyai hiasan dalaman yang klasik. Selain daripada menikmati hidangan makanan yang enak di Restoran Belangkas Selera Sedili, mereka turut melakukan aktiviti dalaman memanjat batu .

programme.title: Selipar Jepun Stileto Merah
programme.desc: Roy semakin merasakan dirinya melakukan kesilapan untuk mengahwini Stila. Bersama-sama Datuk Azhar, dia berpakat untuk memperbaiki hubungan Leto dan Stila. Stila mendapat tahu akan hal itu dan kekal mahu meneruskan rancangan perkahwinan mereka. Namun, Roy enggan bersetuju dengan rancangan itu. Walaupun Airis tahu Leto masih menyimpan perasaan terhadap Stila, dia enggan melepaskan Leto dan tetap mahu meneruskan rancangan perkahwinan mereka. Pada hari perkahwinan itu, Leto mendapat panggilan telefon daripada Roy yang memberitahunya bahawa Stila akan ke luar negara. Leto cuba mengetepikan hal itu, namun, selepas Yani memdedahkan suatu rahsia besar kepada Leto, dia tahu bahawa dia harus bertemu Stila buat kali terakhirnya...

programme.title: Cinta Tanpa Henti
programme.desc: Salina@ Sally mengamuk, Hajar mempertahankan dirinya. Hajar beritahu dia hanya hantarkan laporan kewangan. Sally bagi amaran pada Arman untuk berhenti menggatal, dia tidak teragak-agak untuk menuntut cerai dan meminta ayahnya memecat Arman sebagai CEO Edruce Airlines. Zakiah terdengar gossip mengenai Hajar dan Arman. Hajar pada mulanya bersikap dingin dengan Zakiah, berpura-pura baik kerana teringatkan kata-kata Arman bahawa Zakiah berhak mengambil tindakan tata tertib terhadap mereka jika didapati bersalah. Zakaria juga terpaksa menafikan hubungan mereka kerana tidak mahu karier Zakiah terjejas. Arman cuba menjauhkan diri dari Hajar sementara waktu. Sejak kebelakangan, Mak Hawa kurang sihat. Zakiah mahu bawanya ke klinik tetapi Mak Hawa menolaknya. Rahim semakin akrab dengan Syifa dan Haikal, kadangkala bertanyakan tentang mama mereka. Syifa beritahu mamanya bangun awal dan kurang tidur kerana banyak dapat tempahan menjual cookies dan kek batik secara online. Rahim kemudian tempah kek dari mama mereka melalui Syifa. Mahani jugak pelik suaminya nampak berubah sejak kehadiran Syifa dan Haikal. Rahim terharu setelah merasa kek Maya, dia teringatkan Maya pernah buat kek batik semasa hari ulangtahunnya dan Mahani dahulu. Maya terkejut terima jumlah bayaran kek yang begitu banyak. Syifa cuba mengelak untuk menjawab, begitu juga Hisyam. Mereka juga terpaksa berdalih tentang baju-baju baru yang mahal, kononnya papa belikan separuh harga. Sally pulang dengan keadaan marah setelah mengetahui kebenaran bahawa Arman menjalin hubungan dengan Hajar. Haikal tersungkur jatuh tangga ditolak Sally.

programme.desc: Natasya hanya berkelulusan SPM tetapi bijak, agak lasak dan adakala lebih bersifat seperti lelaki. Namun sesekali dia berdandan dan bersolek, pastinya kebanyakan pemuda kampung akan terpikat dengan kecantikan yang dimiliki oleh Natasya dan memanggilnya Puteri Gunung Ledang. programme.title: Superhero Hati S1
programme.desc: Bagi meredakan keadaan Akasyah terus memperkenalkan Suhana sebagai guru tadi Adam, namun itu membuatkan Zaza teringat nama Suhana dari kolej dan terus mempersendakannya. Lalu Akasyah cepat-cepat menawarkan untuk menghantar Suhana pulang, membuatkan Zaza makin bengang dan semakin galak mengejeknya. Akasyah meminta maaf kepada Suhana bagi pihak Zaza yang biadap, namun Suhana bersahaja mengatakan dia dah biasa. Ini membuatkan Akasyah makin tak keruan dan tidak dapat menghilangkan bayangan Suhana dari memorinya.

programme.title: Biar Aku Jadi Penunggu S1
programme.desc: Hubungan antara Afeet dan Iffat masih hambar, mereka masih tidak bersama semasa tidur. Selain itu, mereka juga bersiap untuk berpindah ke rumah sendiri. Sebaik mereka tiba di rumah baharu, Iffat merungut, dia tiada pernah berkesempatan menduduki rumah itu sambil menyindir Affet yang sekali pun tiada menghubunginya selepas memaklumkan ketibaannya di luar negara. Di dalam rumah, Iffat mempersoalkan kenapa dia ditipu. Afeet hanya menjawab bagaimana dia dan Damia porak peranda selepas berkahwin setahun dan Aqil dilahirkan. Iffat tidak puas hati soalannya tidak dijelaskan. Perhubungan mereka agak tegang tetapi masing dapat mengawal diri. Afeet pula sentiasa merayu dan memohon agar memberikan dia peluang kali ini dan berjanji akan membahagiakan mereka. Dalam pada itu, Iffat menegaskan tentang Rafaal tidak wajar dipersoalkan langsung kerana dia hanya menepuk sebelah tangan.

programme.title: Selipar Jepun Stileto Merah
programme.desc: Selepas menghadapi pelbagai pancaroba, Stila dan Leto berjaya melangsungkan perkahwinan. Namun, disebabkan percanggahan di antara mentua, uapcara perkahwinan mereka itu menghadapi sedikit masalah, lebih-lebih lagi, apabila Airis membuat kunjungan mengejut. Selepas perkahwinan, hubungan Stila dan Leto terus tercabar dek campurtangan mentua. Datin Fairuz terus cuba mempengaruhi Stila untuk menjadi ketua rumah. Sementara Mak Tini dan Pak Wan pula mahu memastikan anak lelaki mereka itu tidak terlalu dipengaruhi oleh keluarga mentua. Hubungan di antara Leto dan Yani juga bertambah buruk selepas itu, apabila Amelia mula menjadi batu api.

programme.title: Cinta Tanpa Henti
programme.desc: Rahim terkejut Haikal baring tidak sedarkan diri. Sofia beritahu mamanya, Salina@ Sally tolak Haikal. Haikal dibawa ke hospital dan dimasukkan ke unit kecemasan. Hisyam dan Sumayyah@ Maya bergegas ke hospital setelah menerima berita itu. Maya tidak menyangka akan bertemu dengan keluarganya di hospital. Maya kecewa dan merajuk Hisyam merahsiakan semua itu darinya. Maya tolong ingatkan Hisyam, papanya pernah buangnya dari keluarga dan tidak perlukan mereka lagi. Mahani juga berkecil hati suaminya melindungi hal itu darinya. Sally mengesyaki Maya mengatur anak-anaknya untuk dapatkan semula kedudukan dalam keluarga itu. Dia yang juga tertekan dengan Arman meminta Arman menceraikannya tetapi dihalang Tn Rahim. Malam itu, Hisyam mendapat panggilan dari Zakiah, doktor mengesahkan Mak Hawa meninggal kerana demam denggi. Hisyam kesal dan bersedih kerana tidak sempat pulang menjenguk ibunya semasa sakit. Arman dapat tahu, Haikal & Syifa adalah anak Maya dan Sally telah menolak Haikal. Dia ceritakan hal itu kepada Hajar. Sally bertemu Hajar dan beri amaran, sebaliknya Hajar membalas bahawa dia tahu tujuan Sally untuk membolot harta keluarga sehingga Maya dibuang keluarga dan kemudian membalas dendam dengan menolak Haikal. Sally telah melawat Haikal di hospital dengan niat jahat. Sejurus kemudian, Hisyam menerima panggilan telefon.

programme.title: J.K.K S5
programme.desc: Salman meminta cuti selama 2 minggu daripada Pak Kodi atas urusan peribadi. Pak Kodi mengupah seorang pekerja sambilan bernama Husin (Jiggy Masin) untuk membantunya di warung. Suatu hari, muncul seorang gadis bernama Dr. Natasha (Aprena Manrose) yang dikatakan dapat membantu memulihkan kaki Salman.

programme.title: BOOM S1

programme.title: Puteri Gunung Ledang S1
programme.desc: Natasya hanya berkelulusan SPM tetapi bijak, agak lasak dan adakala lebih bersifat seperti lelaki. Namun sesekali dia berdandan dan bersolek, pastinya kebanyakan pemuda kampung akan terpikat dengan kecantikan yang dimiliki oleh Natasya dan memanggilnya Puteri Gunung Ledang. Natasya berimpian menjadi model terkenal. Setiap kali mencuba nasib, dia gagal dan akhirnya bekerja sebagai kerani di sebuah agensi peragaan sahaja. Nasibnya berubah apabila dia menjadi duta produk kecantikan secara tidak sengaja. Ramai yang mula jatuh hati dan terpikat pada kecantikan Natasya termasuklah majikannya Rayyan. Rayyan seorang lelaki yang kacak tetapi bersikap ‘kaki perempuan’. Mereka berkenalan secara lebih dekat tetapi Natasya meletakkan tujuh syarat untuk membuktikan cintanya.

programme.title: Selipar Jepun Stileto Merah
programme.desc: Selepas menghadapi pelbagai pancaroba, Stila dan Leto berjaya melangsungkan perkahwinan. Namun, disebabkan percanggahan di antara mentua, uapcara perkahwinan mereka itu menghadapi sedikit masalah, lebih-lebih lagi, apabila Airis membuat kunjungan mengejut. Selepas perkahwinan, hubungan Stila dan Leto terus tercabar dek campurtangan mentua. Datin Fairuz terus cuba mempengaruhi Stila untuk menjadi ketua rumah. Sementara Mak Tini dan Pak Wan pula mahu memastikan anak lelaki mereka itu tidak terlalu dipengaruhi oleh keluarga mentua. Hubungan di antara Leto dan Yani juga bertambah buruk selepas itu, apabila Amelia mula menjadi batu api.

programme.title: Superhero Hati S1
programme.desc: Terkejut dengan kebiadapan Zaza, Suhana telah bergegas pulang ke kampung dan mengadu pada ibunya. Namun ibunya, Sarimah, mengingatkan Suhana bahawa adiknya, Suraya, yang masih belajar di kolej memerlukan bantuan kewangan darinya. Ini membuatkan Suhana terpaksa mencekalkan jiwanya untuk berhadapan dengan cabaran di KL. Sekembalinya ke KL, Suhana cuba sehabis baik menjauhi Akasyah, namun Adam terus menerus memerlukan perhatiannya. Menjelang hujung minggu, Adam telah menelefon Suhana dan merayunya agar menyertai keluarga Adam berkelah di PD. Apabila Suhana menolak, Adam ambil keputusan untuk tidak pergi juga. Ini membuatkan Suhana serba salah, lalu mengalah dan ikut keluarga Akasyah berkelah di PD.

programme.title: Biar Aku Jadi Penunggu S1
programme.desc: Mereka masih berbahasa 'kau' dan 'aku' dan masih tidak tidur bersama. Iffat akui terasa bersalah bersikap sedemikian. Dalam pada itu, Affet terus meminta maaf kepada Iffat. Iffat sentiasa menyambut baik sambil menyatakan "Insyaaalah". Sesekali Iffat memang merasai yang suaminya amat kacak dan menyayanginya. Affet mula bertugas di sebuah firma peguam dan salah seorang kakitangan mengenalinya iaitu rakan baik Damia. Iffat masih berhubung dengan rakan lamanya seperti Lokman dan isterinya Hayati, Isha dan juga Rafaal yang masih ada 'hati' terhadapnya. Iffat seperti simpatinya terhadap Rafaal mencadangkan akan mencari jodoh kepadanya. Lantaran itu, Iffat bersama rakan lain telah sertai pertemuan santai dan minum bersama. Aqil hadir bersama Iffat dan seolah-olah ingin memperkenalkan Aqil kepada Rafaal.

programme.title: Jangan Benci Cintaku
programme.desc: Rofeeka Huda (Feka) dan Shahrizal (Shah) telah disatukan direstui oleh kedua belah pihak ibu bapa mentuanya. Nek Pah menentang perkahwinan merek. Bagi Nek Pah, Feka langsung tidak memenuhi ciri-ciri isteri yang solehah. Feka mahu menikmati hidupnya terlebih dahulu, bersantai. Shah seorang suami yang penyabar dan tidak pernah mendesak Feka. . Tingkahlaku Feka kadangkala membuatkan Shah menyirap juga. Setiap hari, Shah akan bangun dulu sebelum Fika. Dalam pada itu, rakan baik Feka dan Damia iaitu Irwan masih berhubung dengan mereka, khususnya Feka. Irwan sebenarnya mencintai Feka. Tetapi bagi Irwan dia berpegang akan terus berkawan. Tanpa pengetahuan ibu dan bapa Feka, juga Shah, Feka dan Damia merancang untuk melanjutkan pengajian. Mereka dapat Universiti di Perth, Australia. Ibu dan bapa Feka tidak setuju. Manakala Shah hatinya begitu, tetapi menyatakan bersetuju hanya semata-mata mahu mengambil hatinya.

programme.title: Halalkan Hati Yang Ku Curi S1
programme.desc: Delisha tidak selesa dengan kehadiran rakan-rakan Faiq semasa bercuti menyebabkan Delisha ingin pulang bercuti. Rakan-rakannya merancang untuk aktiviti berlumba kereta secara haram, Delisha setuju. Sebelum memulakan aktiviti mereka dipintas polis. kedua-dua mereka ditahan. Tiba-tiba, nenda dan ibu bapa Delisha terpaksa bergegas menjamin keluar Delisha dan Faiq dari lokap. Di balai, Zainal yang menghubungi polis bertemu nenda. Zainal berhasrat nenda berterima kasih. Tetapi nenda marah-marah terus meminta Zainal beredar sahaja. Di rumah, nenda Delisha begitu marah kepada Delisha dan beranggapan Delisha berduaan semasa bercuti. Delisha menjelaskan cara dia bercuti. Nendanya tidak setuju dan rasa kesal menyelesaikan kad kredit Delisha. Kemudiannya, Delisha dan Faiq setuju mereka tidak akan bertemu sementara ini.

programme.title: Maria Terindah S1
programme.desc:
Semua orang terkejut dengan berita Serina membunuh diri. Aris beritahu Fahad yang Serina memang sering terganggu sejak kebelakangan ini dan memang pernah berkali kali cuba untuk membunuh diri. Jihan beritahu Aris, kes Serina mengingatkan dia kepada Maria. Jihan nak tahu kalau Aris ada apa apa kaitan dengan hal Serina. Aris mengaku tidak ada kaitan, tapi takut ada orang yang cuba sabotaj dia. 

Kaki Syafiq semakin teruk kerana cedera dan patah dalam. Syafiq terus tak sedarkan diri. Kawan Syafiq cuba hubungi Indah untuk mintak tolong. 

Jihan jumpa beg Maria dalam bilik Fahad. Dia mula tertanya-tanya. Jihan tanya Fahad apa hubungan Fahad dan Maria. Kenapa beg Maria ada dengan Fahad? Fahad kata dia simpan beg itu sebab itu je kenangan dengan maria yang dia ada. 

Indah mula dikejar taiko dadah. Mereka mahu tahu di mana Syafiq. Indah mintak tolong Aris untuk bantu Syafiq. Aris dan Indah pergi carik Syafiq, tanpa sedar yang mereka diekori taiko dadah. Aris dipukul dan Indah ditahan. 

Aris jumpa Syafiq dan mereka jumpa video Indah di seksa kerana Syafiq. Dua dua panic. Mereka perlu bertindak segera. Aris minta bantuan seorang penyiasat dan pembunuh upahan. 

Aris dan pembunuh upahan menyerang kem taiko dadah. Semua tumpas dan Indah ditembak.

programme.title: Gila Baby
programme.desc: Bob memerlukan wang yang banyak bagi membiayai kos pembedahan ayahnya di hospital. Dengan mengambil jalan mudah, Bob membantu Roy, bekas teman sekelasnya di sekolah yang selalu membulinya dahulu untuk melakukan jenayah mencuri kereta. Walaupun percubaan pertama Bob untuk aktiviti jenayah tersebut berjaya tetapi ada seorang bayi di tempat duduk belakang kereta yang dicurinya itu! Bob kini mendapati dirinya diburu oleh beberapa pihak yang tidak akan berhenti selagi Bob dan bayi tersebut tidak ditangkap! Untuk mengeruhkan lagi keadaan, dalam perjalanan menyelamatkan diri, Bob bertemu Jaja yang mengugut Bob untuk membawanya sekali kerana ingin lari dari masalahnya sendiri.

programme.title: Amukan Pocong S1
programme.desc: Episod mengisahkan Tok Sayut, Sulaiman dan penghulu bermesyuarat untuk menyelesaikan masalah pocong ini. Tepat tengah malam, ketika pocong sedang hendak mendapatkan mangsa ke 13nya, Long Husin bagaikan terpanggil untuk pergi ke paya tersebut. Awang juga tidak dapat berbuat apa-apa, kerana apa juga kuasa yang ada padanya, dapat ditewaskan Tok Sayut. Jasad Long Husin yang ditakluki Awang turut tewas.

programme.title: Cicakman 2
programme.desc: Profesor Klon yang jahat kembali, bukan sahaja untuk menggulingkan Kerajaan tetapi juga untuk mengawal bekalan air tawar dunia melalui rancangannya yang bijak, "Air Hitam". Apabila planet biru kita hanya mempunyai 72 jam sebelum menjadi hitam, Cicakman datang untuk menyelamatkan. Tetapi dia bukan sahaja berhadapan dengan pembunuh upahan artistik Profesor Klon "Rrama\.

programme.title: Bopeng
programme.desc: Bo (Nabil Ahmad) dan Peng (Johan As'ari) merupakan dua orang sahabat baik yang tinggal bersama dan bekerja di sebuah restoran makanan segera yang sama iaitu Opiel Secret Pizza. programme.title: Bodyguard
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Ryan berjaya memujuk Nasha dan Mak Jah bergambar. Gambar ini ditunjukkan kepada Dato' Amir. Ryan dibayar ganjaran RM50 ribu kerana berjaya mengesan Mak Jah. Mereka juga menyewa rumah lain untuk Mak Jah. Dalam kes berasingan, Farish sebagai bodyguard bersama Adam meneruskan latihan persilatan dengan datuknya. Perhubungan Adam dengan Hanis semakin mesra. Danial sebagai bodyguard Eliza telah mendapat rahsia Rashid dan Amran. Mereka pernah bersamasama melakukan penculikan ke atas Eliza. Dengan sebab itu Eliza mengambil keputusan tidak lagi mahu berhubung dengan Rashid, Amran pula telah diberhentikan kerja. Rahul sebagai bodyguard Maya memberi amaran kepada Mikhail supaya tidak lagi berjumpa dengan Boboy tetapi Boboy masih berkeras mahu berjumpa dengan ayahnya Mikhail. Diakhir episod, Eliza diculik oleh Amran semasa Rahul bodyguardnya keluar mengambil barang yang tertinggal dari dalam kereta.

programme.title: Sori: Voice From The Heart
programme.desc: A father searching for his missing daughter finds a satellite that remembers sounds from across the world. Using his daughter's voice as a beacon, the satellite helps him track her down.

programme.title: She'S On Duty
programme.desc: In order to catch a gangster, a cop goes undercover as a high school girl to get close to the gangster's daughter.

programme.title: The Exclusive: Beat The Devil'S Tattoo
programme.desc: When a journalist discovers that his exclusive story on a serial killer was based on false information, he fabricates more lies to cover his mistake.

programme.title: Heung-Boo: The Revolutionist
programme.desc: Set in the Joseon dynasty, a satirical street play becomes popular among the people. Heung-boo, its author, gains fame and is sought by conflicting powers who want to use him for their own agendas.

programme.title: The Age Of Blood
programme.desc: The once best swordsman in Joseon, Kim Ho, was demoted as a prison guard after a lost battle and fought with a rebel force that snuck into the jail to save their captured leader.

programme.title: Toxic
programme.desc: Based on a true story, <Toxic> depicts the truth behind millions of mysterious death happened only in Spring.

programme.title: Parasite
programme.desc: An unstoppable string of mishaps awaits when greed and class discrimination threaten the newly formed symbiotic relationship between the wealthy Park family and the destitute Kim clan.

programme.title: South Bound
programme.desc: Choi Hae-gap has a family who will stand by his decisions given any scenario. As a team, they fight the government's plans to build a resort on the island of their ancestors.

programme.title: Actionhero
programme.desc: A college student dreaming to be an action star discovered an admission fraud. He decided to make an action film of him against the corrupted professor.

programme.title: The Con Artists
programme.desc: A wily safecracker is forced to help a mob boss pull off a $150 million heist, but smells a double-cross in the works.

programme.title: Love Guide For Dumpees
programme.desc: Two recently dumped singles spend a wild drunken night together to get over their exes, then agree to meet nine more times before promising never to see other again.

programme.title: I Am The King
programme.desc: A runaway prince meets a slave who bears a strikingly similar appearance to himself. The prince gets mistaken as the slave and the slave is crowned as King.

programme.title: Baseball Girl
programme.desc: A young girl is graduating from high school and determined to become the first female player to join a professional baseball in Korea.

programme.title: Anarchist From Colony
programme.desc: The true story a Korean patriot Park Yeol, who formed the anarchist organization "Black Wave" during the Japanese colonial period and attempted the assassination of the Japanese Crown Prince Hirohito.

programme.title: Our School'S E.T.
programme.desc: Seong Geun is content with being a P.E teacher, but the school wants to sack him in favor for an English teacher. To survive, he must teach English - but he doesn't speak a word of it.

programme.title: Miss Granny
programme.desc: Complications and hilarity ensues when a 70-year-old woman living unhappily with her son's family is magically restored to her beauty of 50 years earlier.

programme.title: Yoga
programme.desc: Hyo-jung is insecure about her appearance. She joined the yoga academy wishing to restore beauty, yet strange things begin to unfold...

programme.title: Detective K: Secret Of The Lost Island
programme.desc: Joseon's top detective Kim Min attempts to track down the criminals responsible for circulating large amounts of counterfeit silver bullion while in search of the missing sibling of a young girl.

programme.title: Vanishing Time: A Boy Who Returned
programme.desc: A 13-year-old boy goes missing after venturing into a cave in a forest with his friends and later mysteriously reappears a few days later as man in his 30s.

programme.title: Kingmaker
programme.desc: A politician met a talented campaign strategist who helped him in becoming the strongest presidential election candidate. Yet conflicts deepen as the he disagrees with the latter on his ideologies.

programme.title: Love+Sling
programme.desc: Despite having zero interest in the sport, Sung-woong trains to become a top wrestler with his dad's enthusiastic support. When the girl he likes falls for his dad, they begin wrestling for love.

programme.title: iWalker-Moving Kitchen (M)
programme.desc: Tuesday "iWalker" has been upgraded and changed the name into "iWalker-Moving Kitchen". James and the pretty chef, Rachel will move to different province with the mobile kitchen which costs more than 2 million NTD, and introduce to the audience the unique taste of the province.

programme.title: Taste of Life (T)
programme.desc: Ep.767, 768 - Chu-Tsai,Chao and his wife Chin-hsiu,Li have five children. Devoted all his life into developing soy sauce products, Chu-Tsai very much hopes that one of his kids can follow his footsteps and take over his business, but he also respects their own passions and aspirations. Because of their father’s invention dream, the Chao brothers’ lives are about to change…\nChin-Pang,Chou used to be Chin-Hsiu’s lover, and has been Chu-Tsai’s long-time business rival. Seeing Chu-Tsai not only successfully keep the patents of soy sauce products, but also has all the support and assistance from his children, Chin-Pang, filled with bitterness, has been crushing and attacking Chu-Tsai in every way. Hsin-Ta, Chu-Tsai’s eldest son, couldn’t bear to see his father suffer, so he quit his job to take over the family business. To everyone’s surprise, Chu-Tsai discovers that Hsin-Ta is actually Chin-Pang’s son! Finding out that the enemy is actually his biological father devastated Hsin-Ta, and this also drives a wedge between Chin-pang and his son Hsiao-Ming, as he feels threatened.\nChu-tsai’s second son Ying-kai has always set his goal to reach the top of his career. Vacillating between Mei-mei and Ying-hui, Ying-kai also finds himself caught in between the feud of two families; however, this opens new business opportunities for him. On the other hand, Hsin-ta fulfills Chu-tsai’s dream; but he is more confused than ever about family love and romance love… All he knows is that with the family’s support, his determination and conviction, he can build a future of his own!

programme.desc: Ep.4475, 4476 - The Tradition Story of Taiwan presents a series of tales and folktales in Taiwan that have been pass down from one generation to another generation.

programme.title: Taste of Life (T)
programme.desc: Ep.769, 770 - Chu-Tsai,Chao and his wife Chin-hsiu,Li have five children. Devoted all his life into developing soy sauce products, Chu-Tsai very much hopes that one of his kids can follow his footsteps and take over his business, but he also respects their own passions and aspirations. Because of their father’s invention dream, the Chao brothers’ lives are about to change…\nChin-Pang,Chou used to be Chin-Hsiu’s lover, and has been Chu-Tsai’s long-time business rival. Seeing Chu-Tsai not only successfully keep the patents of soy sauce products, but also has all the support and assistance from his children, Chin-Pang, filled with bitterness, has been crushing and attacking Chu-Tsai in every way. Hsin-Ta, Chu-Tsai’s eldest son, couldn’t bear to see his father suffer, so he quit his job to take over the family business. To everyone’s surprise, Chu-Tsai discovers that Hsin-Ta is actually Chin-Pang’s son! Finding out that the enemy is actually his biological father devastated Hsin-Ta, and this also drives a wedge between Chin-pang and his son Hsiao-Ming, as he feels threatened.\nChu-tsai’s second son Ying-kai has always set his goal to reach the top of his career. Vacillating between Mei-mei and Ying-hui, Ying-kai also finds himself caught in between the feud of two families; however, this opens new business opportunities for him. On the other hand, Hsin-ta fulfills Chu-tsai’s dream; but he is more confused than ever about family love and romance love… All he knows is that with the family’s support, his determination and conviction, he can build a future of his own!

programme.desc: Depth analysis of the day breaking news headlines to restore the truth inside.

programme.title: Rivals Of Kung Fu
programme.desc: Everyone wants to win the annual Lion Dance Trophy, including Wong Fei Hung. His jealous rivals, led by Master Shen, try to frame Wong by placing a decomposed corpse in his Po Chi Lam clinic. This gives Lu Wei, a corrupted cop, the chance to pile Wong Fei Hung with various criminal charges. Will Wong be able to defeat his enemies once again?

programme.title: The Emperor And The Minister
programme.desc: The ingenious imperial scholar Liu Yung always embarrasses Emperor Chien Lung with his quick wit and gift of gab. The emperor purposely sets him up to solve the seemingly unsolvable. However, Liu Yung resolves it easily with wit and style and foils the emperor’s plot once again.

programme.title: That Fiery Girl
programme.desc: The bandits of Hulu Valley slay the chief of the Mei Clan while searching for a treasure map. In retaliation, Chun from the Mei Clan infiltrates the bandit's fortress to map a way in for the authorities, but ends up falling in love with the bandit leader's daughter, Pearl. While Chun’s plot is uncovered, he receives unexpected help from Pearl.

programme.title: The House Of 72 Tenants
programme.desc: The 72 inhabitants of a dilapidated tenement live under the thumb of a heartless landlady and her sleazy husband. The arrival of a defiant new tenant however, changes their fate. The residents pool their resources together to prevent evictions, deflect targeted harassment by a corrupt policeman and ultimately prevent their home from being sold.

programme.title: Executioners From Shaolin
programme.desc: The White-Browed Priest supports the brutal Qing government, burning down Shaolin Temple and hunting its disciples. Hung from Shaolin falls in love with Fang while escaping from the hunt and the couple have a son before Hung is killed by the Priest. To avenge his father, Hung creates a new form of martial art combining his parents’ kung fu styles.

programme.title: Disco Bumpkins
programme.desc: This musical production showcases personable singer/actor George Lam, who tries to find love and success in the world of TV commercials along with his buddies Hamburger and Snoopy.

programme.title: The Flying Dagger
programme.desc: The Yu family and the Green Dragon clan became enemies when the Yu daughter killed the clan head’s son, who was a rapist and murderer. The Green Dragon leader wounds the head of the Yu family with his flying daggers, and a wandering swordsman saves the family using his own flying dagger skills. However, his allegiances and motives are unclear.

programme.title: The Last Tempest
programme.desc: This sequel to The Empress Dowager continues the tale of Emperor Guangxu and Empress Dowager Cixi. Despite Guangxu’s enthronement, his ability to rule effectively is overshadowed by the ever-present power of Cixi. When his attempts to reform the Imperial system are thwarted by the Empress Dowager, Guangxu attempts to curb her power.

programme.title: Godfather Of Canton
programme.desc: Commissioner Liu Ta-hua (Tsao Ta-hua) is arrested by special envoy Cheng Chih-cheng (Wang Jung) for corruption. Coolie Lin Szu-hai (Gordon Liu Chia-hui), who has unintentionally helped Cheng, is given a small post under Lo. Lin is smart and soon learns how to get dockside bribes. Later, he gets a regular spin-off from Adjutant Chang….

programme.title: The Happiest Moment
programme.desc: In this horror anthology an old man dies from an overdose of virility pills, a cop goes on the run after extorting money from a hooker, and a mortician's ghost goes on the rampage.

programme.title: Killers Five
programme.desc: The Duke’s daughter has been kidnapped by the notorious Golden Dragon Hill bandits. A swordman named Yue Zhen Bei is assigned to save her, and expecting many dangers on the journey, Yue garners help from a group of good friends who are also kung fu masters.

programme.title: Sons Of Good Earth
programme.desc: This is an epic tale set during the time of the Sino-Japanese war. A painter Yu saves a young girl, Lotus, who is being sold to a brothel. They fall in love, get married and settled in to a peaceful life. However, their life is soon shattered by the Japanese invasion and the brutal regime that follows.

programme.title: The Shepherd Girl
programme.desc: In this musical drama, Hsiu Hsiu, a beautiful shepherd girl, falls in love with a handsome boatman Ta Lung. However, she cannot afford to marry him because of her father’s towering debt from gambling. To complicate the matter, a rival suitor promises to pay off all her father's debts on one condition: that Hsiu Hsiu marries him...

programme.title: Love Parade
programme.desc: Fashion designer Shi asks his friend Mui to comment on his new design but is angered by her criticism. When Mui asks him to design a gown for her to attend a gala event, Shi takes revenge by making a clown costume instead. Seeing Mui’s embarrassment, Shi feels guilty and apologizes to her, before they fall in love….

programme.title: Mist Over Dream Lake
programme.desc: A young girl Chen is sent away by her parents who are going through divorce, to stay with the Changs. On the Chang’s farm, she meets their daughter Ling Yun, the eldest son Ling Hsiao, and a young artist Hsu, and spends a summer with them that she will never forget.

programme.title: The Adventures Of Emperor Chien Lung
programme.desc: Emperor Chien Lung travels incognito to Jiangnan to review his people’s livelihood but soon discovers that corrupt officials are oppressing his people. The emperor meets an upright young man and they join hands to teach the corrupt officials a lesson. The young man was appointed as his bodyguard thereafter.

programme.title: Dirty Ho
programme.desc: Master Wang, who is actually the 11th prince, poses as an antique connoisseur to hide his true identity. When he meets Dirty Ho, a witty con artist, Wang knows he has found the right man to help him untangle a royal succession plot...

programme.title: Forever And Ever
programme.desc: Ivy Ling Po plays a young scholar who is manipulated into marrying a nobleman's reluctant daughter. After marrying, he soon discovers the reason for her hesitation. She is stricken with a contagious disease. But, with the power of true love, their romance prevails.

programme.title: The Golden Seal
programme.desc: Dai Tian Chou practices martial arts since young so he can avenge his father’s death. He meets Wu Xiao Yan who is disguised as a man one day and is suddenly beaten by a group of gangsters. Wu begs her father to allow her to take Dai back home to recover. Little does Dai know this is his chance to take revenge.

programme.title: Big Times For The Crazy Bumpkins
programme.desc: Ah Niu finds a bag of jewels on the street and becomes rich. It is at this time that Uncle Zhou asks him to sign a contract to marry a girl, but it turns out to be a trap for Ah Niu to sell his house. In the end, Ah Niu becomes poor again….

programme.title: The Rebel Intruders
programme.desc: Thousands of displaced refugees rush to the southern towns to avoid the civil war in north China. Three such young men trained with martial arts skills become sworn brothers, and accidentally got involved in the battle of the rebel leaders in town when they save a refugee girl. Can they fight back against the rebel gangs?

programme.title: A Friend From Inner Space
programme.desc: A young boy whose parents are separated tries to find happiness. One day, he meets and befriends a kind hearted spirit Ren, who decides to make him truly happy by getting his parents back together.

programme.title: Death Duel
programme.desc: Third Master is a renowned swordsman in the martial arts world, but the constant challenges by other swordsmen compel him to fake his death and pursue a secluded life. This does not prevent others from seeking him out to challenge him however, and he is forced to return to fight his way till the end.

programme.title: The Scandalous Warlord
programme.desc: General Feng occupies the city of Shandong, and soldiers and civilians alike welcome him without knowing his tyrannical and lustful nature. His first official business is to inspect the brothels and take the prostitutes home to become his concubines. Feng is finally killed by his officers, but will the new general rule the city differently?

programme.title: The Protectors
programme.desc: Ling Hsiao and Kuan Wang Lung are two guard chiefs working for an old convoy master. Lung is secretly in love with Fang Yen, the master’s granddaughter but Yen is attracted to Ling Hsiao instead. In order to win her back, Lung sets up a trap to steal the convoy and frames Ling Hsiao for it.

programme.title: Dead End
programme.desc: Uninhibited youth Chun meets a rich girl Wen when her car breaks down and drives her home. Chun falls in love with Wen but Wen’s brother dislikes him and forbids his sister to see him. He humiliates Chun and gets Chun beaten up, so Chun takes the pistol he has found accidentally on the street to Wen’s home and shoots her brother dead.

programme.title: Vengeance Of A Snow Girl
programme.desc: A crippled woman seeks vengeance against the four men who killed her parents. However, when she crosses path with a young warrior who falls in love with her, trouble ensues as his father is one of the killers responsible for her family's massacre years ago.

programme.title: Heroes Of Sung
programme.desc: Heroes Of Sung stars one of the original kung fu ladies of the silver screen, Shih Szu, who plays swordswoman Meng Hung. She must work with Fan Tien-Fu, played by Lo Lieh to find and protect the royal seals of the Sung Dynasty. Shih's magnificent performance earned her the female hero role in another hit Dracula And The 7 Golden Vampires.

programme.title: The Black Lizard
programme.desc: Young swordsman Lung Fei encounters strange omens portending the death of his fiancé. His enquiries with the help of Chief Constable Tieh Hu reveal an astounding story, in this tale of men and women struggling to save their true loves.

programme.title: The Millionaire Chase
programme.desc: It's a fun and wild romp that mixes pleasure with pleasure. A nightclub owner, playboy Peter Chen Ho, has his ways with three sisters while gallivanting across Asia. Each one has a dangling relationship to save - ensuring a series of mishaps and comic moments.

programme.title: Brave Archer And His Mate
programme.desc: Guo Jing and Huang Rong raise the son of his sworn brother Yang Kang and named him Yang Guo. To prevent Yang Guo from taking revenge for his father’s death, Huang Rong bans him from learning martial arts. Yang Guo runs away from home in anger and encounters Ouyang Feng, who teaches him the “Toad Stance” and accidentally unveils his true identity….

programme.title: Young Lovers
programme.desc: Guitar-playing rich kid, Yang Fan, heads to Japan to join a rock 'n' roll band where he soon finds himself competing for the affections of two beautiful girls.

programme.title: The Tigress Of Shaolin
programme.desc: Sam is being hunted as he discovers that the mayor and the chief of medical bureau are colluding with a drug dealer. He is saved by a fishermen family and works in their friend’s grocery but the grocery owner is killed when the enemies track Sam down. Sam escapes to Shaolin to learn the cudgel style of kung fu in order to avenge his friends.

programme.title: The Bride Napping
programme.desc: A rich girl Yue Ying, together with her maid Chun Lan, encounter a poor scholar Bian Ji at a fête. Chun Lan realizes Yue Ying is in love with him, but mixes his identity with a bandit due to an old servant’s confusion, threatening the couple’s union. After a series of complications, misunderstandings and mismatches, Chun Lan finally saves the day.

programme.title: Kid From Kwangtung
programme.desc: After many years as a respected actor (The Chinese Boxer) and action choreographer (Jackie Chan's Drunken Master), the Shaw Studio finally gave the dependable and commendable Hsu Hsia a chance to direct his own movies. He didn't waste the opportunity, inviting three other kung-fu designers to help on this fight-filled thriller. Wang Yu, co-star of such classics as Dirty Ho and The Kid With A Tattoo, here takes center stage as a young rascal caught between an anti-Ching Confederation and violent, vengeful Ching troops. But when he discovers that the good guys are led by master martial arts actor Jen Shih-kuan (Once Upon A Time In China) and the bad guys are led by the incredible Huang Cheng-li (Snake In The Eagle's Shadow) everyone knows that loads of great kung-fu is in store.

programme.title: The Amorous Lotus Pan
programme.desc: Adapted from the renowned Chinese novel, The Water Margin, this is the story of a poor and beautiful girl Lotus Pan, who is raped by her master and had to be married off to a midget who treats her badly. Lost and lonely, Pan unwittingly becomes a pawn in the game of lust between her husband’s playboy brother Wu Song, and a murderous man Men Ching.

programme.title: Heaven Sword And Dragon Sabre
programme.desc: In the Yuan Dynasty, martial artists everywhere battle for the Heaven Sword and the Dragon Sabre, as only when these two powerful weapons combine can a secret be revealed to help one become the king of the martial arts world. As Zhang Wu Ji acquires the skills from “Nine Yang Scriptures” by chance, he is also embroiled in this lengthy battle.

programme.title: Hex Vs Witchcraft
programme.desc: A compulsive gambler with bad luck owes money to a violent gangster boss and trades his wife as down payment, causing her to leave him. As he decides to kill himself, a mysterious old man offers him a proposal to marry the ghost of his dead daughter in exchange for cash and an expensive apartment.

programme.title: The Lady Hermit
programme.desc: The Lady Hermit is hiding for years, plotting revenge after she has been defeated by the sinister Black Knight. Shaolin Handlock is a lethal go-getter who begs Lady Hermit to teach her, hoping to slay the demon herself. The Black Knight's days are numbered as the Lady Hermit and her protege perfect the technique to take him down.

programme.title: Black Magic
programme.desc: Hsu Lo is up against an evil black magic practitioner San Kan Mi, who wants to place a death spell on him and a love spell on his fiancée Wang Chu Ying. Fortunately, Wang's friends manage to find another veteran witch doctor to take on the evil San. This bone-chilling tale of good versus evil races to a heart-stopping ending.

programme.title: Dawn Will Come
programme.desc: Liang Cai drugged the beautiful Qiu Rong and raped her, but promised to marry her after getting his parent’s consent. Since then, there is no news of his proposal and Qiu Rong confronts Liang Cai when she finds herself pregnant. This is when she discovers that he has already married a rich noble girl and even plans to kill her….

programme.title: When The Clouds Roll By
programme.desc: Su is a schizophrenic who refuses to believe that her pilot lover is killed in a plane crash and makes up stories to deal with things. She runs into an old classmate Lai, who is also a doctor one day, and he finds ways to treat her illness. Su slowly recovers and accepts the reality, as well as her newfound love.

programme.title: Africa's Underwater Wonders 1 - Mafia Island - Uncharted Paradise
programme.desc: Just off the Tanzanian coastline lies an island Utopia. Its diverse habitats provide homes for a multitude of creatures living above the water and below. And when the time is right, a mysterious being rises from the deep to feed in the rich waters. This is Mafia Island.

programme.title: Ocean Parks 1 - Monterey Bay Marine Sanctuary
programme.desc: On the West Coast of the United States, the Monterey Bay National Marine Sanctuary is the largest marine sanctuary in the country - home to 525 species of fish, and a massive, underwater Kelp forest.

programme.title: Wild Pacific Rescue 1 - Baby Sea Otter Finds a Family
programme.desc: Join the vet and his team in saving a massive sea lion caught in a plastic noose, and then visit the Rescue Center, where a harbor seal pup may lose its eyesight and a baby sea otter needs a risky but life-saving surgery.

programme.title: Wild Pacific Rescue 1 - Battle to Save a Sea Lion
programme.desc: Battle wind and waves to find a sea lion trapped in a plastic ring. Then visit the rescue center, where over 80 orphan seals must be fed several times a day to prepare for release into the wild, and see an Amazonian duck get a miraculous operation.

programme.title: Wild Pacific Rescue 1 - One Very Lost Sea Turtle
programme.desc: Follow the team in healing and releasing a grumpy sea turtle, and then meet a sea lion with an unusual injury that must be taken by crane to the rescue centre. Find out how the vet aids an aging fruit bat and a community rescues a one-eyed seal pup.

programme.title: Kingdom of the Tide
programme.desc: Low tide exposes a band of shore called the intertidal zone. It’s a place of stunning extremes, attacked by hurricane force waves and exposed to baking heat. Creatures here have evolved in countless bizarre ways. Scientists explore this alien realm.

programme.title: The Ocean's Greatest Feast
programme.desc: Get a front-row seat to the planet’s biggest biomass migration, the annual 1,000-mile sardine run along South Africa’s east coast. See billions of these tiny fish run a gauntlet of hungry predators, including stealthy seals and dive-bombing gannets.

programme.title: Great Blue Wild 2 - Costa Rica - Shark Defenders
programme.desc: The Pacific coast of Costa Rica is a biodiversity hotspot that hosts nearly 5,000 species of marine life. But here in this undersea jungle, the ocean’s top predator is at risk. Discover how marine defenders are teaming up to save the shark.

programme.title: Great Lakes Wild 1 - The Goby Effect
programme.desc: The Lake Erie Watersnake is currently on the brink of extinction, and researchers have been fighting to get it back. And it looks like it's finally working - thanks to the round goby. Grad student Lizzy Mack is heading out on day trips to catch bucket loads of the snakes, collect measurements, and inject them with small microchips to track them along their way, all while dodging bites from some of the crankiest snakes around.

programme.desc: The islands of the Bahamas are ringed with lush coral, underground cave systems, and plunging barrier reefs. Beyond the white sands and turquoise water, marine life abounds: agile reef sharks, large whitetip sharks, manatees, sea turtles, and wild dolphins.

programme.desc: A dam is an engineering feat, controlling massive amounts of water. But it can also wreak havoc on the animals that call those waters home.

programme.title: Reef Wrecks 1 - Reef Wrecks of Roatan
programme.desc: This island of the coast of Honduras stands out as a vacation resort hot spot. But it’s not just the sun and sand that brings the tourists in droves. It’s actually a diver’s paradise with shipwrecks scattered from all corners of the the island.

programme.title: Great Blue Wild 1 - Belize
programme.desc: More than 200 caves play host to an unmatched array of marine life and coral formations in this underwater kingdom 40 kilometres from Belize City. It's a deep blue wilderness brimming with rare, exotic fish, eagle rays, sharks, and huge green morays.

programme.title: Africa's Underwater Wonders 1 - Lake Malawi
programme.desc: In one of Africa’s greatest lakes, rock and water set the stage for evolution’s most magnificent display. This episode tells the story of this remarkable example of evolution in action, as well as showing how the lake provides for a range of life, both above and below the surface.

programme.title: Ocean Parks 1 - The Mesoamerican Reef
programme.desc: The Mesoamerican Reef is a pristine ocean ecosystem- but after decades of overfishing and tourist activity, much of this reef is in jeopardy. These Parks are monitored by Ocean advocates dedicated to maintaining the shark feeding grounds, turtle populations and marine spawning grounds that line this incredible reef system.

programme.title: Arabian Seas 1 - Carnivores of the Coral Garden
programme.desc: The seas are alive with carnivores. Meet the sharks and rays who patrol the coral reefs, hunting down their prey. Learn about toxic fish who disguise themselves to ambush the unwary, and armoured predators who devour vulnerable targets.

programme.title: Arabian Seas 1 - Magicians of the Reef
programme.desc: Arabia’s coral reefs are home to some of nature’s most impressive illusionists. Creatures can pulsate with colour, transform in the blink of an eye, or perform riveting displays of showmanship. Because in these dangerous waters, disguise is crucial.

programme.title: Shark Squad 1 - Chasing Mako
programme.desc: In some of the most-remote regions on the planet, researchers dive deep and brave danger to unlock secret shark behaviours, challenge myths about sharks, and fight for the protection of these supreme predators – before it’s too late.

programme.desc: Sharks are among the planet’s oldest and most highly evolved predators. These people do all they can to find safe ways of living with sharks.

programme.title: Great Lakes Wild 1 - Creatures of the Night
programme.desc: Flying squirrels leaping through the air is quite a sight - especially for researchers who know they’re not supposed to be here. The Southern flying squirrel, typically found along the shores of Lake Erie, is now moving its territory up towards Lake Ontario and beyond thanks to warmer winters.

programme.title: Great Lakes Wild 1 - Back from the Dead
programme.desc: Sometimes animals get a second chance. Like the majestic elk, which went extinct in Ontario thanks to habitat loss and over-aggressive hunting. But a few years ago, hundreds of elk were brought back, to re-populate the province in four different areas. Some floundered because of new, aggressive local predators. But a colony of elk in Burwash, on a former prison ground, is thriving.

programme.title: Reef Wrecks 1 - Mexico's Artificial Reefs
programme.desc: From opportunistic pirate ships, to well-armed navy vessels, Mexico’s Yucatan Peninsula is steeped in maritime history.

programme.title: Great Blue Wild 1 - Cozumel
programme.desc: Clear waters, deep reefs, dangerous caves, and tunnels draw divers to the island of Cozumel on Mexico’s east coast. The Caribbean Sea port is home to multicoloured schools of fish, bull sharks, and gigantic sea turtles.

programme.title: Africa's Underwater Wonders 1 - Bazaruto Shallows
programme.desc: Off the coast of Mozambique, warm water surrounds idyllic islands. In this shallow realm, sunlight fuels abundant growth. Rich sea currents carry food and inundate underwater meadows. Life in many forms crowds the space between seabed and surface.

programme.title: Ocean Parks 1 - Bahamas Exuma Cays
programme.desc: The Exuma Cays are a remote wonder: hundreds of tiny islands extending south from the Bahamian Capital of Nassau. In the 1950’s, developers dreamed of developing this pristine, and largely unexplored region. But before construction could begin, the Bahamian government supported an expedition to chart the cays. They liked what they saw, and in 1959 established the Bahamas National Trust, creating the Bahamas’ first Ocean Park.

programme.title: Arabian Seas 1 - Island Feast
programme.desc: Off the coast of Oman, summer weather drives nutrients in from the ocean depths where they meet the Arabian sun, causing an explosion of life. Smaller fish spawn, filling the waters with eggs. This creates a buffet predators just can’t resist.

programme.title: Arabian Seas 1 - Defenders of the Reef
programme.desc: It’s summer in the Gulf of Oman. The scorching Arabian sun heats the shallow waters to 86 degrees boosting the growth of algae across a vast coral reef. This attracts thousands of hungry herbivores creating a fish versus fish turf war.

programme.title: Arabian Seas 1 - A Turtle's Legacy

programme.title: Ocean Parks 1 - Bahamas Exuma Cays
programme.desc: The Exuma Cays are a remote wonder: hundreds of tiny islands extending south from the Bahamian Capital of Nassau. In the 1950’s, developers dreamed of developing this pristine, and largely unexplored region. But before construction could begin, the Bahamian government supported an expedition to chart the cays. They liked what they saw, and in 1959 established the Bahamas National Trust, creating the Bahamas’ first Ocean Park.

programme.title: Great Lakes Wild 1 - Back from the Dead

But a few years ago, hundreds of elk were brought back, to re-populate the province in four different areas. Some floundered because of new, aggressive local predators. But a colony of elk in Burwash, on a former prison ground, is thriving.

programme.title: Wild Wild East 1 - Tides

programme.title: Great Blue Wild 2 - Palau Shark Sanctuary
programme.desc: Palau is a tiny country with a big story. In 2009, this island nation in the middle of the western Pacific Ocean created the world’s first shark sanctuary to protect more than 100 shark species from reckless overfishing and the brutal practice of commercial shark finning. Then, in 2014, Palau once again led the way. It established the world’s largest marine sanctuary – a no-go zone for foreign commercial fisheries nearly the size of California.

programme.title: Great Blue Wild 1 - Roatan
programme.desc: Home to Earth’s second-largest barrier reef, Roatán is one of the world’s top dive spots–known for its rare black coral, low-lying nurse sharks, and fearsome-looking barracuda.

programme.title: Tinga Tinga Tales
programme.desc: Why Parrot Can'T Keep A Secret - You see there was a time when Parrot was the best keeper of secrets in the whole of Tinga Tinga. Infact Parrot couldn't open his beak at all! Then one day some beast dares to steal Lion's mane and Parrot sees the whole thing! But how is going to tell Lion?! Tales from Africa.

programme.title: Tinga Tinga Tales
programme.desc: Why Bushbaby Has Big Eyes - You see there was a time when Bushbaby didn't have big eyes. She had tiny little eyes and she was always getting lost. Strange things begin to happen and there are stories that Majitu the Great Giant has returned to Tinga Tinga. Young Bushbaby doesn't believe a word of it... and convinces the other animals that Majitu the Giant does not exist. "If you can't see him, he's not real". But then she does see the Giant and her eyes grow big as planets. Tales from Africa.

programme.title: Noddy Toyland Detective
programme.desc: The Case Of The Moving Train Tracks - Queen Sparklewings is having a fairy picnic in Fable Forest that evening. Everyone offers to help set up for the picnic but Queen Sparklewings tells them not to worry – the fairies can do it all. Later, when Noddy and all his friends are approaching Fable Forest Station on the train they discover someone has redirected the train tracks. They can't get to Fable Forest. How will they have the picnic in time? Noddy needs to investigate why the train tracks have been moved. With the help of Bumpy and Revs, Noddy follows the clues and discovers that the train tracks were moved by Fairy Coco who was tired to having to do all the work for Queen Sparklewings. If no one came to the picnic at all, there'd be no tidying up to do. Fairy Coco tells the Queen that she's very sorry for causing a mess and the Queen tells her that she's sorry too. She didn't mean to make the Fairies do all the work and miss out on the fun! Later, the picnic takes place and everyone helps clear up afterwards. It's much quicker and much more fun if everyone helps out together! Good job Noddy!

programme.title: Noddy Toyland Detective
programme.desc: The Case Of The King Of Toyland - Noddy returns from a Make and Take party at Pat-Pat's and finds the Builders are constructing a big orange palace in Toy Green. by order of the King of Toyland! Noddy decides to investigate: who is the mysterious King of Toyland? He spots the Knights carrying a royal litter, but all he can see inside is the top of an orange crown. Realising the King's favourite colour must be orange, Noddy remembers seeing Pat-Pat painting a bowl of oranges and wonders if she knows who the King is. Pat-Pat doesn't but following the clue of a cut out crown shape in orange card and using his investigative skills Noddy works out that Cloppycorn is the King of Toyland. He was fed up being bossed around by Hoof and Bling so decided to be king for the day with a little help from Queen Sparklewings. Bling and Hoof are sorry for upsetting Noddy and everyone is friends again in time for the Royal Ball! Well done Noddy. Case closed!

programme.title: Guess With Jess
programme.desc: What’S Happened To My Little Tree? - Jess shows us his little tree: a beautiful flowering shrub in full bloom. He tells us that his little tree didn't always look like this...there was a time when the tree's leaves turned yellow! What's happening to my little tree? That's the Big Question! Jess asks Mimi for help, but she's in bed with a bad cold. She's drinking lots of fluids to help make her better. Jess gives his little tree some more water to help make it better but when he goes to check on his tree the next day the leaves have turned brown and crinkly! Baa and Billie come along - Billie is tucked in the brim of Baa's woolly hat, it's too cold for her to come out. Jess wonders if his little tree is cold and needs warming up. So he wraps a potato sack round the little tree. But the next day things are even worse the leaves are falling off.! And it's happening all over Greendale Farm! Jess goes to see Horace who is busy composing a new song. It's all about the Seasons. Jess finally realises that what's happening to his tree is perfe.

programme.title: Guess With Jess
programme.desc: How Can We All Keep Cool? - It's the day of Mimi's dance in Jess's barn but its too hot to move, let alone dance. Jess wonders how they can all keep cool! That's the BIG QUESTION. Jess asks his friends for ideas. Horace keeps cool by swimming under water, but that's no good for Jess and everyone else who can't swim. The puppies keep cool by panting, but that just makes Jess even hotter and out of breath. And Willow keeps cool by standing very still. That won't work for a dance, they can't all keep still! Mimi comes past holding a little fan which makes a lovely cool breeze. Jess realises that what they need is a giant fan that could make a cool breeze in the barn. He and Mimi make a huge fan which Horace works as part of his one-man band. Everyone has a great time dancing and keeping cool. Jess has answered the Question. Yippety Yay!

He sees a funny creature with a round head, a long tail and a little mark on his nose. “What's the funny little creature in the pond?” Hey! That's the Big Question! The creature has vanished so Jess describes it to Mimi who draws a picture of it. Mimi, Joey and Jinx think it must be a fish and name him Freddie, but Jess is not so sure. Time passes and Jess doesn't see Freddie again for ages. When he does spot him he's grown two back legs! Jess decides he needs a closer look using Billie's magnifying glass. They search for Freddie all round the pond. Baa thinks he's found him, but it turns out to be a newt, with four legs and spots on its back. At that moment a small frog jumps out onto a lily pad. It has the white mark on its nose just like Freddie but this is a frog! What's happened wonders Jess. Horace comes back and explains that frogs start out as tadpoles and gradually change, growing legs and losing their tail.

programme.title: Guess With Jess
programme.desc: How Can We Keep Dry For Horace'S Concert? - Horace has planned a big musical show but before it can start it begins raining and everyone runs for shelter. How can we keep dry? What are they going to do? Mimi walks by with her umbrella. She's lovely and dry. They all try to crowd under it but it's not big enough. We need to build a BIG umbrella says Jess.
